  <brief_title>The Effect of Viral Load on Intrahepatic Recurrence in Hepatitis B Virus (HBV)-Related Hepatocellular Carcinoma (HCC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Cohort Study of the Effect of Serum HBV DNA Level on Intrahepatic Recurrence in Locally Treatable, HBV-related HCC Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
