  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of serum hepatitis B virus (HBV) DNA
      level on intrahepatic recurrence in locally treatable hepatocellular carcinomas (HCCs)
      related with HBV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective cohort study

      Survival

        -  Overall survival rate

        -  Disease free survival rate

      Recurrence

        -  Cumulative recurrence rate
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
