  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Child-Pugh Class A or B

          -  Maximal tumor size less than 5 cm

          -  No previous history of treatment for hepatocellular carcinoma

          -  Recurrent hepatocellular carcinoma located more than 2 cm from the previous cancer
             site and is found more than 1 year's gap

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hepatocellular carcinoma in portal vein

          -  Hepatocellular carcinoma in hepatic vein
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
